Title: Maryada Ramanna
Writer: S.S. Kanchi (story & dialogues), Vara Mullapoodi (story idea), S.S. Rajamouli (screenplay)
Plot: A man returns to his parents' village to claim his land. Along the way, he befriends a charming young woman. Unbeknownst to him, her family has a long-standing feud with his family.
